description:
Add storage capacity to your Thule® Child Carrier. The console has a built-in cup holder and a handy zippered pocket to stash snacks or your phone.

  • Cup holder fits cups big or small
  • Zippered pocket with a headphone port
  • Works with Thule® Chariot Cross and Chariot Lite Single Child Carriers, as well as Thule® Urban Glide 2 and Glide 2 strollers
  • Not compatible with Thule® Cheetah, Cadence and Coaster series child carriers
name: Thule Organizer Sport
